He did.

113
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:25,000
As long as the visitor
says the paraphrase,

114
00:05:25,319 --> 00:05:26,839
we will help with all our might.

115
00:05:27,839 --> 00:05:29,800
You two have been talking

116
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:32,759
and claimed to be from the Prajna Hall
and the Bodhi Department.

117
00:05:32,879 --> 00:05:34,319
Why didn't you say the paraphrase?

118
00:05:34,432 --> 00:05:34,959
No.

119
00:05:34,959 --> 00:05:36,120
I was so worried.

120
00:05:36,399 --> 00:05:36,920
Wait.

121
00:05:37,519 --> 00:05:38,759
Don't you know

122
00:05:38,759 --> 00:05:40,759
you are guarding a treasure here?

123
00:05:42,639 --> 00:05:43,199
Treasure.

124
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,199
Treasure!

125
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,639
The pigs are the treasure.

126
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:55,488
Senior brother.

127
00:05:57,199 --> 00:05:57,728
You are smart.

128
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:02,800
Muqing.

129
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:05,000
You don't have to say anything, Bufan.

130
00:06:05,319 --> 00:06:06,399
I made you a promise

131
00:06:06,399 --> 00:06:07,360
and I will keep my word.

132
00:06:09,279 --> 00:06:10,759
I have decided not to be a swordsman.

133
00:06:11,319 --> 00:06:12,600
Those things have no use to me.

134
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:15,199
There's a long life ahead.

135
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:17,879
You will go to travel
to many places, right?

136
00:06:18,439 --> 00:06:19,519
You can abandon the main altar.

137
00:06:20,079 --> 00:06:21,079
But you need money

138
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:23,000
and also those martial arts books.

139
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:24,680
Whatever you want

140
00:06:24,839 --> 00:06:25,800
will all still be yours.

141
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:28,759
Muqing.

142
00:06:33,199 --> 00:06:34,439
You truly are a gentleman.

143
00:06:38,319 --> 00:06:40,079
But I'm afraid I can't meet you

144
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:41,480
at Futu Temple tonight.

145
00:06:42,199 --> 00:06:42,720
Besides,

146
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:46,680
I also wish
you can find the Altar Treasure soon.

147
00:06:48,759 --> 00:06:50,000
Where will you go?

148
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:52,720
Where should I look for you
after I obtain the secret treasure?

149
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:00,120
Meixun.

150
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:03,279
Meixun.

151
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:05,319
If you go there,

152
00:07:05,959 --> 00:07:07,959
I will definitely treat you
to a cup of Queshe tea.

153
00:07:09,319 --> 00:07:11,000
I'll certainly go for that cup of tea.

154
00:07:13,639 --> 00:07:14,319
Bufan.

155
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:15,879
Take care.

156
00:07:19,079 --> 00:07:19,680
Take care.

157
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:21,079
Take care.

158
00:07:25,639 --> 00:07:26,279
Let's go.

159
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:49,040
Are you planning to return to Meixun?

160
00:07:49,439 --> 00:07:50,079
Yes.

161
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,000
I left when I was young,

162
00:07:52,439 --> 00:07:53,439
and haven't returned since.

163
00:07:53,959 --> 00:07:55,639
I can hardly remember
what Meixun looks like.

164
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:58,279
Then let's find a place
for you to recuperate.

165
00:07:58,800 --> 00:07:59,720
When you've recovered,

166
00:08:00,079 --> 00:08:01,319
we'll look for Men Sandao.

167
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:05,360
How do you know I will go to him?

168
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:08,240
You never like to owe others.

169
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:10,120
Men Sandao helped you today.

170
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:12,279
You surely want to do something

171
00:08:12,279 --> 00:08:13,199
to return the favor.

172
00:08:15,879 --> 00:08:17,279
He calls me Bufan now.

173
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:18,800
And I call him Muqing.

174
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:21,360
Who says the swordsmen and the officials

175
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:23,040
cannot be friends?

176
00:08:24,879 --> 00:08:26,319
I don't understand what he wants to do.

177
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:28,319
But whatever it is,

178
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:29,920
I want to follow him.

179
00:09:11,519 --> 00:09:12,159
Mr. Zhuo.

180
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,919
We aren't done yet.

181
00:09:25,559 --> 00:09:26,112
Jialuo.

182
00:09:28,639 --> 00:09:29,799
Can you spare my life?

183
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:33,240
Let you get away

184
00:09:35,639 --> 00:09:36,679
once again?

185
00:09:37,799 --> 00:09:39,440
My Rongtian Sword Sect is disbanded.

186
00:09:39,919 --> 00:09:41,559
And my senior brother
Yu Huanjie is dead.

187
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:43,799
I have given the Discipline Seal
to Men Sandao.

188
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:47,240
Can't you just put this to an end?

189
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:48,559
End?

190
00:09:50,679 --> 00:09:52,080
Has the Dagu murder case ended?

191
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:55,799
Has my master's death ended?

192
00:10:00,159 --> 00:10:02,279
Today, it's not about whether you want
to fight with me or not.

193
00:10:03,279 --> 00:10:05,639
It's that your Rongtian Ridge disciples
have committed a grave crime,

194
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:07,519
and you, as their leader,
cannot shirk the blame.

195
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:14,759
Today, I must bring you to justice.

196
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:18,320
So, today

197
00:10:19,799 --> 00:10:21,519
you want me dead, right?

198
00:10:25,279 --> 00:10:26,000
Yes.

199
00:10:27,679 --> 00:10:29,919
The Dagu murder case
was the doing of Yu Huanjie.

200
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:32,279
Bufan was also very outraged.

201
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:33,879
Rongtian has already disbanded.

202
00:10:33,879 --> 00:10:35,320
There is no longer such a sect.

203
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:38,399
May you show mercy

204
00:10:38,759 --> 00:10:40,159
and spare our lives?

205
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:42,919
We will no longer hold the swords

206
00:10:43,519 --> 00:10:45,440
and will live out our days in peace.

207
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:46,559
And what about my master?

208
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:49,600
Was my master a swordsman?

209
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:52,559
He was just a madman.

210
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:55,320
What did he have to do with you?

211
00:10:57,480 --> 00:10:59,960
He was living a quiet and mundane life
in retirement.

212
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,679
Did you think of sparing his life

213
00:11:02,320 --> 00:11:04,000
when you killed him?

214
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:08,360
Sir.

215
00:11:09,799 --> 00:11:11,200
Please spare us.

216
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:16,600
Huo Qin.

217
00:11:17,399 --> 00:11:18,000
Huo Qin.

218
00:11:18,592 --> 00:11:19,168
Get up.

219
00:11:19,168 --> 00:11:19,712
I won't get up.

220
00:11:19,712 --> 00:11:20,240
Don't beg him.

221
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:20,919
I have to.

222
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:21,759
You didn't do wrong.

223
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:22,679
Don't beg him.

224
00:11:24,159 --> 00:11:24,759
Bufan.

225
00:11:27,559 --> 00:11:28,080
Wang Jialuo.

226
00:11:29,879 --> 00:11:31,399
I'll take responsibility
for what I've done.

227
00:11:32,279 --> 00:11:33,039
But remember,

228
00:11:33,799 --> 00:11:35,279
this has nothing to do with Huo Qin.

229
00:11:35,279 --> 00:11:36,360
Leave her out of this.

230
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,679
No matter what,

231
00:11:38,879 --> 00:11:40,080
if you lay a finger on Zhuo Bufan,

232
00:11:40,399 --> 00:11:41,600
you have to step over my dead body.

233
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:42,120
Huo Qin.

234
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:43,559
Today, I only want Zhuo Bufan.

235
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:45,600
If you insist on stopping me,

236
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:47,039
according to the Qing Code,

237
00:11:49,088 --> 00:11:49,696
we can kill you.

238
00:11:49,696 --> 00:11:50,200
Wang Jialuo.

239
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:50,960
Then kill me!

240
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:51,520
Huo Qin.

241
00:11:52,919 --> 00:11:53,840
You far outnumber us.

242
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:55,440
What kind of man are you?

243
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:56,120
Huo Qin.

244
00:11:56,120 --> 00:11:57,320
Does hiding behind a woman

245
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:59,679
make him a man?

246
00:12:01,279 --> 00:12:01,879
