255
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:00,600
Was it you who fired the gun?

256
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:02,336
Yes.

257
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:04,960
Zhuo Bufan and Huo Qin.

258
00:14:06,519 --> 00:14:07,399
