you were right to kill.

263
00:14:37,919 --> 00:14:39,360
But we had an agreement.

264
00:14:39,519 --> 00:14:40,600
He gave me the seal.

265
00:14:40,600 --> 00:14:41,759
He cooperated with us.

266
00:14:42,159 --> 00:14:43,960
You should have kept your words.

267
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:44,799
Mr. Muqing.

268
00:14:45,559 --> 00:14:46,879
