271
00:14:51,840 --> 00:14:53,559
but you can't be that cold-blooded.

272
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:01,840
I beg to differ.

273
00:15:04,879 --> 00:15:06,679
I've told you that something
was wrong with your woman.

274
00:15:06,679 --> 00:15:08,000
But because she is your woman,

275
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:09,519
I have never captured
and interrogated her.

276
00:15:15,159 --> 00:15:16,559
You should've done it!

277
00:15:18,039 --> 00:15:19,519
After you told me, I investigated her.

278
00:15:21,360 --> 00:15:22,240
Lin Anjing

279
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:25,840
was a spy under Sei I Shinpu's command.

280
00:15:29,679 --> 00:15:30,879
I have already

