00:37:37,320 --> 00:37:38,079
Liu Lin.

565
00:37:40,320 --> 00:37:40,960
Liu Lin.

566
00:39:03,440 --> 00:39:04,800
What's the use of chanting scriptures?

567
00:39:06,039 --> 00:39:07,199
She told me

568
00:39:07,679 --> 00:39:08,480
her ideals

569
00:39:08,480 --> 00:39:10,559
was to see this country change.

570
00:39:12,440 --> 00:39:15,119
She believed that
there would be a new China.

571
00:39:16,599 --> 00:39:17,679
If possible,

572
00:39:18,000 --> 00:39:19,320
I hope they can witness

573
00:39:19,320 --> 00:39:21,920
the future's new China.

574
00:39:24,159 --> 00:39:25,000
If you believe it,

575
00:39:25,239 --> 00:39:26,039
it will happen.

576
00:39:27,760 --> 00:39:28,440
I believe it.

577
00:39:29,119 --> 00:39:29,920
If you believe it,

578
00:39:30,719 --> 00:39:31,719
then make it happen.

579
00:39:32,880 --> 00:39:33,559
I will.

580
00:39:35,880 --> 00:39:36,400
Muqing.

581
00:39:39,480 --> 00:39:40,320
I will too.

582
00:39:41,320 --> 00:39:43,000
Together, we will change the world.

583
00:39:45,079 --> 00:39:47,199
But I only have
the Bodhi and Discipline Seal.

584
00:39:47,800 --> 00:39:48,840
Lin Haohan is dead.

585
00:39:49,679 --> 00:39:50,840
Prajna Seal.

586
00:39:54,760 --> 00:39:56,400
Isn't Wu Shuangbao still alive?

587
00:40:01,599 --> 00:40:02,239
Muqing.

588
00:40:04,079 --> 00:40:05,360
Only Wang Jialuo isn't here.

589
00:40:07,199 --> 00:40:08,039
He said

590
00:40:08,360 --> 00:40:09,800
that he would come here tonight.

591
00:40:10,944 --> 00:40:13,472
(Futu Temple)

592
00:40:49,199 --> 00:40:49,760
You're here.

593
00:40:53,880 --> 00:40:54,599
Where is Mr. Lin?

594
00:40:55,440 --> 00:40:56,119
Hasn't he arrived?

595
00:41:00,639 --> 00:41:01,199
Jialuo.

596
00:41:01,760 --> 00:41:02,760
Let's talk.

597
00:41:03,800 --> 00:41:04,400
About what?

598
00:41:06,840 --> 00:41:07,392
Okay.

599
00:41:08,639 --> 00:41:09,199
Let's talk.

600
00:41:27,239 --> 00:41:30,000
You are an imperial constable.

601
00:41:31,039 --> 00:41:32,960
I am an imperial guard.

602
00:41:33,719 --> 00:41:34,240
That's right.

603
00:41:35,599 --> 00:41:37,039
We are both servants of the court.

604
00:41:39,159 --> 00:41:40,440
You are a Dharma inheritor.

605
00:41:40,800 --> 00:41:42,119
I am a Bodhi inheritor.

606
00:41:42,760 --> 00:41:44,480
We are both from Southern Shaolin.

607
00:41:45,599 --> 00:41:46,400
Sort of.

608
00:41:46,960 --> 00:41:48,519
Not sort of.

609
00:41:48,719 --> 00:41:49,719
If there's no legacy,

610
00:41:49,719 --> 00:41:51,000
how can you become a constable?

611
00:41:51,000 --> 00:41:52,000
And how can I become a guard?

612
00:41:54,440 --> 00:41:55,840
Sir, what do you mean?

613
00:41:58,559 --> 00:42:00,159
What I mean is,

614
00:42:00,760 --> 00:42:03,800
shouldn't a disciple
follow the master's orders?

615
00:42:07,840 --> 00:42:08,679
Of course.

616
00:42:09,440 --> 00:42:10,320
Good.

617
00:42:10,656 --> 00:42:11,239
Master's order...

618
00:42:11,239 --> 00:42:12,760
But if the order goes against the court,

619
00:42:12,760 --> 00:42:14,280
I will not obey.

620
00:42:15,079 --> 00:42:15,599
Sir.

621
00:42:16,599 --> 00:42:17,800
The sect is our home.

622
00:42:18,320 --> 00:42:19,280
The court is the nation.

623
00:42:19,880 --> 00:42:20,880
The nation must come first.

624
00:42:23,880 --> 00:42:26,320
The court doesn't always
stand for the nation.

625
00:42:26,440 --> 00:42:27,639
It is so under normal circumstances.

626
00:42:27,760 --> 00:42:29,000
This nation is...

627
00:42:29,000 --> 00:42:29,760
Mr. Muqing.

628
00:42:29,960 --> 00:42:30,679
How can you say

629
00:42:30,679 --> 00:42:32,000
such rebellious and outrageous words?

630
00:42:37,559 --> 00:42:38,280
Forget it.

631
00:42:38,280 --> 00:42:38,800
Never mind.

632
00:42:39,840 --> 00:42:40,352
No.

633
00:42:40,800 --> 00:42:41,639
We must talk it through.

634
00:42:42,119 --> 00:42:42,760
No.

635
00:42:43,079 --> 00:42:44,608
I have nothing to talk with you.

636
00:42:44,608 --> 00:42:45,199
It's just that...

637
00:42:45,199 --> 00:42:46,280
I shouldn't have talked to you.

638
00:42:46,280 --> 00:42:47,480
I am stupid.

639
00:42:48,679 --> 00:42:49,719
Just stupid.

640
00:42:49,719 --> 00:42:51,280
You are just obstinate.

641
00:42:51,280 --> 00:42:51,920
Come on.

642
00:42:51,920 --> 00:42:52,519
Let's fight!

643
00:42:56,559 --> 00:42:57,519
Why?

644
00:42:58,000 --> 00:42:58,599
Wang Jialuo.

645
00:42:58,599 --> 00:42:59,800
Let me put it bluntly.

646
00:42:59,800 --> 00:43:02,039
The treasure belongs to Southern Shaolin.
It's not the court's.

647
00:43:02,199 --> 00:43:04,199
Our masters are both
from Southern Shaolin.

648
00:43:04,639 --> 00:43:06,519
They are the owners
of the Altar Treasure.

649
00:43:06,519 --> 00:43:07,559
What they wish

650
00:43:07,559 --> 00:43:08,960
is that the court cannot have it.

651
00:43:08,960 --> 00:43:10,360
It must be given to the rightful person.

652
00:43:14,960 --> 00:43:17,000
All under heaven is the emperor's land.

653
00:43:17,480 --> 00:43:19,159
Since it is within the borders
of the Qing Dynasty,

654
00:43:19,159 --> 00:43:20,440
then it belongs to the Qing Dynasty.

655
00:43:21,199 --> 00:43:22,280
If not to the court, to whom?

656
00:43:22,280 --> 00:43:23,199
Who is the rightful person?

657
00:43:23,559 --> 00:43:24,840
Those rebels from Tongmenghui?

658
00:43:25,800 --> 00:43:27,039
Men Sandao, what's wrong with you?

659
00:43:27,119 --> 00:43:28,039
Have you lost your mind?

660
00:43:28,039 --> 00:43:29,719
I think it's you
who have lost your mind.

661
00:43:29,719 --> 00:43:31,760
Do you know what I used to do
back in the days?

662
00:43:31,880 --> 00:43:34,280
I was the guard
by the late Emperor's side.

663
00:43:34,280 --> 00:43:35,599
I could even enter the imperial study.

664
00:43:35,599 --> 00:43:37,800
I joined the reform
with the late Emperor.

665
00:43:37,800 --> 00:43:39,360
Do you know what the reform means?

666
00:43:39,360 --> 00:43:40,679
It's about changing the world.

667
00:43:41,159 --> 00:43:43,320
I was a reformist back then.

668
00:43:43,559 --> 00:43:45,320
Now, Tongmenghui
also wants a revolution.

669
00:43:45,320 --> 00:43:46,480
They want to change the nation.

670
00:43:46,480 --> 00:43:48,519
I will give the Altar Treasure to them!

671
00:43:48,519 --> 00:43:49,199
Men Sandao!

672
00:43:50,599 --> 00:43:52,360
You are outrageous.
According to the Qing Code...

673
00:43:52,360 --> 00:43:53,400
Cut the crap.

674
00:43:53,400 --> 00:43:55,440
What else do you know?

675
00:43:56,000 --> 00:43:57,159
These past days,

676
00:43:57,159 --> 00:43:59,400
I've seen you've got skills.

677
00:43:59,400 --> 00:44:01,360
I wanted to give you a chance
to join the revolution.

678
00:44:01,360 --> 00:44:02,840
Since you deny it,

679
00:44:03,199 --> 00:44:03,800
alright then.

680
00:44:03,960 --> 00:44:04,559
Let's fight!

681
00:44:04,840 --> 00:44:06,119
You asked me to be an imperial guard,

682
00:44:06,119 --> 00:44:07,840
but I refused.
And you said I was ungrateful.

683
00:44:08,800 --> 00:44:10,920
Fortunately,
I did not stoop to your level.

684
00:44:11,400 --> 00:44:13,199
Otherwise, I would have been shameless.

685
00:44:13,519 --> 00:44:14,800
Shameless!

686
00:44:22,599 --> 00:44:24,280
(Dagu County Yamen Constable)
Irgen-Gioro Muqing.

687
00:44:25,119 --> 00:44:26,440
You intend to rebel.

688
00:44:27,400 --> 00:44:28,599
I must execute you.

